{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"RUIHE2","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["The Lucky Crane\n\n<size=45>Chapter 2 - Zuikaku & Her Friends<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","bgm":"story-1","say":"After Zuikaku hurriedly gave me her morning report, we went out together for a walk around the base.","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05}},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Sorry, Commander... I was up all night cramming Offense Skillbooks...","actor":307060},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"... I know, I'll be more careful next time...","actor":307060},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Hey, what's this? Why's everyone gathering at the pier?","actor":307060},{"actorName":"{namecode:76}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"say":"Why, if it ain't Zuikaku! You out for a walk with the Commander?","paintingFadeOut":{"time":0.5,"side":0},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","actor":305030},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Yup! So, why are you all gathered here?","actor":307060},{"actorName":"{namecode:77}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"We wanted to talk to some Eagle Union peeps about a joint exercise, and we're discussing how to bring it up with them.","actor":305040},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Uh, can't you just, like, bring it up with them? Like normal people do?","actor":307060},{"actorName":"{namecode:47}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Ise and Hyuuga could maybe do it, but most of us aren't the types who can just ask someone about a joint exercise...","actor":302090},{"actorName":"{namecode:54}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":-1,"say":"She's right. If someone like Takao or I were to ask them, we'd come off as too formal, and they might speculate that we're up to something...","actor":303020},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Then why don't I do it? I was just about to head their way anyhow.","actor":307060},{"actorName":"{namecode:76}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Really? 'Cause that'd be a huge help.","actor":305030},{"actorName":"{namecode:47}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"If Zuikaku will ask on our behalf, then I'm sure it'll go well.","actor":302090},{"actorName":"{namecode:54}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":-1,"say":"Yeah. Sorry for making you go out of your way like this, Zuikaku.","actor":303020},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"No need to be sorry! I can handle it, no problem!","actor":307060},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Zuikaku went to the Eagle Union dormitory and proposed the joint exercise. Almost everybody she told about it agreed to participate.","dir":1,"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"*Phew*... That about makes it one lap around the base, huh?","actor":307060},{"actorName":"{namecode:96}","bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"blackBg":true,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"This happens surprisingly often~ Like, I'm just out and about, then suddenly somebody asks me for a favor.","actor":307060}]}